&#160;‚Äî &#160;<small><a href="User_Paine_Ellsworth" title="User:Paine Ellsworth"><font color="darkblue"><b><sup>.`</sup></b>^)&#160;</font>Paine&#160;Ellsworth</a><a href="User_talk_Paine_Ellsworth" title="User talk:Paine Ellsworth"><sup>diss`cuss</sup>&#160;<font color="darkblue">(^<b><sup>`.</sup></b></font></a></small>&#160; 12:55, 10 October 2009 (UTC)</p>
<p>Hi, please provide citations for any included countries and not make assumptions which is very misleading and unencyclopedic. --<a href="User_Bardcom" title="User:Bardcom" class="mw-redirect">Bardcom</a> (<a href="User_talk_Bardcom" title="User talk:Bardcom" class="mw-redirect">talk</a>) 20:10, 4 July 2008 (UTC)</p>
<dl>
<dd>Since this is a template, it does not list reference citations, and instead it relies upon the <a href="Wikipedia_RS" title="Wikipedia:RS" class="mw-redirect">verifications</a> utilized in each of the articles to which it links. Happy editing!</dd>
